           ---------+>][ THE BUG BOX!! ][<+---------
 
Here's the deal.. how to make a cheap, easy to use, fone-tap that's small, actually able to be hidden inside a fone, and is powered by the fone line itself.. and if that isnt kickass, the conversation on the line is broadcasted to any fm radio within 100 ft!! All with parts for under $15!! ok'z.. it aint as eazy as it sounds, but it is damn easy.

